Package game.collisions

Package that includes all the collision classes
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    BounceBack
    Class used to detect if the ball touches the small Platforms
    EnemyAttack
    Class used in level3 to attack the NINJA
    EnemyWalk
    Class used to move the Enemy using a collision with the ground
    FireBallDestroy
    Class used to detect if the FireBall touches any of the instances in the if statement.
    MoveBall
    Class used to detect if the ball touches the wall
    NinjaCollisionListener
    Class used to detect all the ninja collisions that can affect the game
    SpawnIceBall
    Class used to spawn or destroy ice ball when collisions happens
    SpawnLava
    Class used to spawn or destroy lava when collisions happens
